# Exclude list for the sample_region partition.
#
# One path per line, relative to the partition root (so `etc/carrier.xml`
# skips /sample_region/etc/carrier.xml). Lines starting with '#' are
# comments; blank lines are ignored. Anything listed here is simply not
# copied into the build image.
#
# Naming convention:
#   <partition>.list         → applied for debug builds
#   <partition>_release.list → applied for release builds
#   <partition>_<custom>.list → applied for debug_<custom> / release_<custom>
#
# So the file for RELEASE builds on this same partition would be
# `sample_region_release.list`.

# Example: drop OEM carrier branding the sample ROM ships with
etc/carrier/carrier-branding.xml
etc/carrier/operator-logo.png

# Example: wallpapers are huge and you want a leaner build
media/wallpapers/oem/
